Question: In at least one image there is a brown rectangle tv with two silver knobs on it.

Reference Answer: False

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a brown rectangle TV in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a brown rectangle TV in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many silver knobs are on the TV?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many silver knobs are on the TV?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2} == 2')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} == 2')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
